  "subject": "Create functions to get ESR info",
  "commit_message": "Create functions to get ESR info\n\nThe ESR portal is used to register VIM information. As part of the\nend-to-end integration the kubeconfig file is expected to be retrieved\nfrom this endpoint. This change implements the functions to comunicate\nwith AAI endpoint.\n\nChange-Id: I20a932cb0417c3ac4f24c0b4760ebfbf47682c9b\nSigned-off-by: Victor Morales <victor.morales@intel.com>\nIssue-ID: MULTICLOUD-470\n",
